<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CUPOD — Online English Communication Academy</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --green: #1DB954;
    --green-dark: #15a046;
    --green-light: #24e066;
    --black: #0a0a0a;
    --dark: #111111;
    --dark2: #1a1a1a;
    --white: #f5f5f0;
    --gray: #888;
    --font-display: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    --font-body: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px 40px;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; align-items: center; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .04em;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--black) !important;
    padding: 9px 22px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700 !important;
    letter-spacing: .05em;
    transition: background .2s, transform .15s !important;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--green-light) !important; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 160px 40px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 80% 20%, rgba(29,185,84,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 10% 80%, rgba(29,185,84,0.08) 0%, transparent 55%),
      var(--black);
  }
  .hero-noise {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.03;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .14em;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    width: fit-content;
    animation: fadeUp .6s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    position: relative;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(72px, 12vw, 160px);
    line-height: .95;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--white);
    animation: fadeUp .7s .1s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    color: var(--green);
    font-style: normal;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);
    color: var(--gray);
    max-width: 520px;
    font-weight: 300;
    animation: fadeUp .7s .2s ease both;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    position: relative;
    display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 40px;
    animation: fadeUp .7s .3s ease both;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--black);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--green-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .04em;
    padding: 15px 36px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
  .hero-stats {
    position: relative;
    display: flex; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    animation: fadeUp .7s .4s ease both;
  }
  .hero-stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 42px;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-stat-lbl { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* TICKER */
  .ticker {
    background: var(--green);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 14px 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .ticker-inner {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: ticker 22s linear infinite;
  }
  .ticker-inner span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--black);
    padding: 0 32px;
  }
  .ticker-dot {
    color: var(--black);
    opacity: .4;
  }

  /* SECTION */
  section { padding: 100px 40px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .18em;
    color: var(--green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: .5px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-body {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--gray);
    max-width: 580px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* HOW IT WORKS */
  .how { background: var(--dark); }
  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }
  .step-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    padding: 40px 32px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background .2s;
  }
  .step-card:hover { background: #202020; }
  .step-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--green);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform .35s ease;
  }
  .step-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 64px;
    color: rgba(29,185,84,0.12);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 26px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: .5px;
  }
  .step-body { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.8; }
  .step-pills { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .pill {
    background: rgba(29,185,84,0.1);
    color: var(--green);
    border: 1px solid rgba(29,185,84,0.25);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  /* PROGRAM */
  .program-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .program-months { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; }
  .month-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border-left: 3px solid transparent;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background .2s, border-color .2s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .month-card:hover, .month-card.active {
    background: #1f1f1f;
    border-left-color: var(--green);
  }
  .month-card.active .month-label { color: var(--green); }
  .month-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 6px; transition: color .2s; }
  .month-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 22px; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .program-detail {
    background: var(--dark2);
    padding: 40px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
    position: sticky; top: 90px;
  }
  .detail-month { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--green); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .detail-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 36px; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .detail-body { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .detail-list { list-style: none; }
  .detail-list li {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--white);
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .detail-list li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */
  .testimonials { background: var(--dark); }
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }
  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    padding: 36px 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .testimonial-card::before {
    content: '"';
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 80px;
    color: rgba(29,185,84,0.15);
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px; right: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .test-stars { color: var(--green); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .test-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 24px; font-style: italic; }
  .test-name { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .test-role { font-size: 12px; color: var(--green); margin-top: 2px; }
  .test-country { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 2px; }

  /* PRICE */
  .price-section { text-align: center; }
  .price-card {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 60px auto 0;
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(29,185,84,0.3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 56px 48px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .price-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green), var(--green-light));
  }
  .price-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--black);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em;
    padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .price-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 90px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .price-period { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .price-features { list-style: none; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .price-features li {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 11px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .price-features li .check {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(29,185,84,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(29,185,84,0.4);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  /* OBJECTIONS */
  .objections { background: var(--dark); }
  .obj-list { margin-top: 50px; max-width: 720px; }
  .obj-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .obj-q {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    gap: 20px;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .obj-q-text { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 22px; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .obj-icon {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(29,185,84,0.3);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    color: var(--green); font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background .2s, transform .3s;
  }
  .obj-item.open .obj-icon { background: var(--green); color: var(--black); transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .obj-a {
    max-height: 0; overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height .4s ease, padding .3s ease;
  }
  .obj-a-inner { padding-bottom: 24px; font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.85; max-width: 620px; }
  .obj-item.open .obj-a { max-height: 200px; }

  /* COUNTRIES */
  .countries { text-align: center; }
  .countries-strip {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .country-tag {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    transition: border-color .2s, color .2s;
  }
  .country-tag:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }

  /* CTA BANNER */
  .cta-banner {
    background: var(--green);
    padding: 80px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-banner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(50px, 8vw, 100px);
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: .95;
    letter-spacing: .5px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .cta-banner p { font-size: 18px; color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 36px; }
  .btn-dark {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
    padding: 18px 44px;
    border: none; border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform .15s, opacity .2s;
  }
  .btn-dark:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); opacity: .85; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 60px 40px 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .footer-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 32px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .footer-logo { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 36px; color: var(--green); letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .footer-tagline { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 8px; max-width: 260px; }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .footer-col h4 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--white); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .footer-col a { display: block; font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray); text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 10px; transition: color .2s; }
  .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .footer-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray); }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes ticker {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  /* REVEAL */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(32px);
    transition: opacity .7s ease, transform .7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 14px 20px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    section { padding: 70px 20px; }
    .hero { padding: 140px 20px 60px; }
    .program-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .program-detail { position: relative; top: 0; }
    footer { padding: 40px 20px 30px; }
    .cta-banner { padding: 60px 20px; }
    .footer-top { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">CUPOD</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#program">Program</a>
    <a href="#how">How It Works</a>
    <a href="#stories">Stories</a>
    <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="#enroll" class="nav-cta">Enroll Now</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-noise"></div>
  <div class="hero-tag">Online English Communication Academy</div>
  <h1>SPEAK.<br><em>LEAD.</em><br>GROW.</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">3 months. 3 sessions a week. One transformative program that turns hesitation into confidence — and confidence into career growth.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#enroll" class="btn-primary">Start Your Journey</a>
    <a href="#program" class="btn-outline">See the Program</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">10+</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-lbl">Countries represented</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">36</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-lbl">Live sessions per program</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">3</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-lbl">Months to fluency</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="hero-stat-num">100%</div>
      <div class="hero-stat-lbl">Online & live</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TICKER -->
<div class="ticker" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="ticker-inner">
    <span>SPEAK WITH CONFIDENCE</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>BUSINESS ENGLISH</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>REAL-LIFE ROLE PLAY</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>GROUP SESSIONS</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>CAREER GROWTH</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>BECOME THE NEXT SUCCESS STORY</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>SPEAK WITH CONFIDENCE</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>BUSINESS ENGLISH</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>REAL-LIFE ROLE PLAY</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>GROUP SESSIONS</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>CAREER GROWTH</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
    <span>BECOME THE NEXT SUCCESS STORY</span><span class="ticker-dot">✦</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="how" id="how">
  <div class="section-label reveal">How It Works</div>
  <div class="section-title reveal">SIMPLE.<br>STRUCTURED.<br>EFFECTIVE.</div>
  <div class="steps-grid">
    <div class="step-card reveal">
      <div class="step-num">01</div>
      <div class="step-title">Join the Community</div>
      <div class="step-body">Enroll online in minutes. You're placed in a live group of driven adults from across the Arab world and beyond — all with one goal: communicate better.</div>
      <div class="step-pills"><span class="pill">Online</span><span class="pill">Live Group</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-card reveal">
      <div class="step-num">02</div>
      <div class="step-title">Train 3× a Week</div>
      <div class="step-body">Three structured sessions every week on Zoom. Every session is interactive — speaking drills, role-play, real conversation. No passive watching.</div>
      <div class="step-pills"><span class="pill">Mon / Wed / Thu</span><span class="pill">Role-Play</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-card reveal">
      <div class="step-num">03</div>
      <div class="step-title">Level Up Monthly</div>
      <div class="step-body">Each month unlocks new skills and a game-based challenge that pushes your communication under pressure — the best way to make it stick.</div>
      <div class="step-pills"><span class="pill">Game Challenge</span><span class="pill">Real Scenarios</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-card reveal">
      <div class="step-num">04</div>
      <div class="step-title">Graduate Ready</div>
      <div class="step-body">After 3 months you leave with fluency in professional English, interview confidence, and a network of peers who keep you accountable.</div>
      <div class="step-pills"><span class="pill">Certificate</span><span class="pill">Career-Ready</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROGRAM -->
